About This Item

Details

  • Variety pack offers plenty of nutritious feeder insects for your toad friend.
  • This feeder bundle provides great staple feeders as well as treats.
  • Can be used to feed a wide variety of medium to large toad species.
  • One bundle can keep two to three toads fed and happy for up to three weeks.
  • Specially packaged to help ensure a live arrival in most weather conditions.

See More

Keep your pet toad in tip-top shape with Josh's Frogs Toad Frog Feeder! This variety pack is designed to keep your toad fed and happy for up to three weeks. Each order comes with 3/4-inch banded crickets, black soldier fly larvae and waxworms. These insects are great for routine feeding as well as treating. And best of all, this bundle is specially packaged to help ensure a live arrival in most weather conditions. Treat your pal to the fresh, nutritious insects they crave with Joshâ€™s Frogs!

                                          • Right to Know/Access, Correct, and Delete Personal Information

                                            Right to Know/Access, Correct, and Delete Personal Information

                                            Right to Know/Access:
                                            If you have a Chewy account, you can access the personal information Chewy has about you by logging into your Chewy Account.
                                            Regardless of whether you have a Chewy Account or not, you can request a report of the personal information Chewy has about you. We'll email you a link to the report within 45 days.

                                            Request a Report

                                            Right to Correct:
                                            If you have a Chewy account, you can access, update or correct the personal information Chewy has about you within your Chewy Account.

                                            Right to Delete:
                                            If you have a Chewy Account, you can delete your Account and the personal information Chewy has about you by logging into your Chewy Account and selecting Privacy Preferences from your Account Settings.
                                            If you do not have a Chewy Account, select the link below to delete any personal information Chewy has about you.
